data.description: **Now offering $5,000 use-as-you-choose!** Welcome to your new home sweet home in the heart of Jacksonville! A charming abode that perfectly embodies the character and convenience of city living. This home offers a unique blend of contemporary elegance and cozy comfort, making it an absolute gem! Step inside and you'll immediately notice the beautiful wood laminate flooring - there's no carpet anywhere! The open layout and natural light beaming in throughout creates an airy ambiance that's sure to delight. The bright white kitchen with granite countertops and sleek subway tile backsplash will make you swoon. To add, the kitchen includes stainless steel appliances and there's even an extra wine fridge in the dining area. Also note, practicality meets peace of mind with the new duct system installed in 2021. For those who love outdoor living, this one has it all. Step out onto the back deck and take in the serenity of your private, fenced yard. Whether it's morning coffee or evening cocktails, this space is your personal oasis to relax and unwind. 106 White Oak also offers a short commute to area bases, shopping, and dining. For the homebody, you'll have the convenience of all the dining apps right at your fingertips! Want coffee but don't want to get dressed to go get it? No problem - Uber Eats can get it for you! This is a luxury denied to those who live further out.This home is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle upgrade. It's a place where you can bask in the elegance of living in an updated space, entertain effortlessly, and enjoy city living with ease. It's a home that radiates charm and character, making it a must-see for anyone seeking the perfect blend of modern convenience and timeless appeal. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this your new home!
